The series was conceived and written by David S. Goyer and developed and produced by the BBC's Adjacent Productions and filmed at Bay Studios in Neath, Port Talbot and Swansea in Wales.
Eight episodes were created for the first season, with the series' U.S. premiere on April 12, 2013.
On April 17, 2013, Starz renewed the series for a second season; with production beginning in mid-year 2013. The new episodes are planned to be broadcast in 2014
